      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair before it can be reliably driven. The interior shows heavy wear with staining, damage, and deterioration throughout. The exterior has visible rust, dents, and paint damage. Suitable for buyers willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts vehicle.",
